description:
Job Responsibilities:

Executing the account strategies to drive market share gain at Brand level or vendor level for Corporate Accounts to exceed the sales plan;
Identifying and develop new business opportunities by developing new customers and maintaining a good relationships with existing customers;
Understanding market and competitive landscape, conducting competitor analysis to formulate the right sales strategies;
Responsible for pricing negotiation with customers for gaining more business and also meet company's margin expectation;
Lead and collaborate with different departments to meet customer needs;
Assist in any ad-hoc projects when assigned.

Job Requirements:

Diploma / Degree holder, preferably in sales and marketing or printing-related disciplines;
Minimum of 1-2 years sales work experience; printing, trims, and packaging will be an advantage;
Good command of spoken and written English, Chinese and Mandarin; and other languages would also be an advantage;
Sales-driven personality, independent, analytical and results-oriented
Good interpersonal, commercial, presentation, and solutions selling skills.

We offer excellent career development opportunities with a highly competitive salary supported by a benefits program including 5-days work, medical, MPF, and sales incentive plan. Interested parties please click "APPLY NOW" for application information.

 **All information collected will be keptstrictly  confidential and solely for recruitment purposes.**

Job Responsibilities :

Responsible to order input and incoming/outgoing goods/material receiving verification;
Coordinate with internal and external parties to ensure orders information are accurate;
Regular reports updating and coordinate with internal departments for the general admin. management;
Other ad-hoc projects as required by department supervisor

Job Requirements :

Good command in both English and Chinese;
Good communication skills, self-motivated and have a good sense of responsibility;
Proficient MS Office application including Excel and Word;

We offer excellent compensation package, promotion prospects and job satisfaction. Interested parties, please email your detailed resume with current and expected salary by click “Apply Now”.

We are an Equal Opportunities Employer. Personal data collected will be used strictly in accordance with the employer's personal data policy, a copy of which will be provided upon request. Candidates who do not notified within 8 weeks after submitting your application may consider the application unsuccessful and the application will be retained up to 24 months.

