Requirement

• Diploma holder or above with 2-3 years working experience;
• Good command of spoken & written English and Mandarin;
• Detail-oriented person with good organization abilities;
• Well verse in Microsoft Excel & Outlook

Job Description

• Monitor and follow up status of the on-line orders;
• Maintain quality communication with customers and provide solutions to resolve customer requests;
• Coordination work with our overseas office on customer care processing;
• Assist on stock monitoring;
• Coordination with suppliers on stock replenishment;
• Work on system data to generate CRM reports and recommendations

* Fresh graduates are welcome *

We work in a nice, modern and convenient office (only 3 minutes walk from Chai Wan MTR station).

APPLY NOW 

Degree Holder or above with 2 years working experience;
Proficiency in Microsoft Excel; Good analytical skills;
Capability to prioritize work and manage several projects at a time;
Communication ability in spoken and written English and Chinese (Mandarin is a MUST);
Prior knowledge in labels and packaging industry will be a plus, but not necessary.

THE JOB

Get brief from Sales team and study product's feasibility;
Select suitable materials and processes;
Calculate costings through existing tools and maintenance of databases;
Maintain relationship & smooth communication with suppliers;
Work closely with HK other teams such Production, Logistic & Merchandising;
European customer oriented
Ad hoc assignments for communication and certification purpose (FSC, OEKO TEX, etc);
Become part of our dynamic team, bring your vision and your energy.

We work in a nice, modern and convenient office (only 3 minutes walk from Chai Wan MTR station).

Please visit our website: www.newsprintgroup.com 

We offer competitive remuneration package with comprehensive fringe benefits to the right candidate. Interested parties, please CLICK the "APPLY NOW" button, and send your resume to us with your last and expected salary.

All personal data collected will be treated in strict confidence and used for recruitment only.
